sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MutWH as Mutating Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ValWH as Validating Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ODH as ODH Notebook Controller
    participant KF as KF Notebook Controller
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant NB as Notebook Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,NB: Flow 1: Notebook Creation (Auth Mode)
    User->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>MutWH: Admission Review<br/>TLS (service cert)
    Note right of MutWH: Sets reconciliation lock<br/>Resolves ImageStream→digest<br/>Injects CA bundles<br/>Injects MLflow env vars<br/>Injects proxy settings
    MutWH-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Notebook
    K8sAPI->>ValWH: Validation Review<br/>TLS (service cert)
    ValWH-->>K8sAPI: Allowed

    Note over ODH: ODH controller reconciles first
    ODH->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount, ConfigMap<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token
    ODH->>K8sAPI: Create kube-rbac-proxy Service (8443)<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token
    ODH->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token
    ODH->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding (auth-delegator)<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token
    ODH->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute (parentRef→gateway)<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token
    ODH->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant (cross-ns)<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token
    ODH->>K8sAPI: Remove reconciliation lock annotation<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token

    Note over KF: KF controller sees lock removed
    KF->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet (replicas=1)<br/>with kube-rbac-proxy sidecar<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token
    KF->>K8sAPI: Create Service (80→8888)<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA token

    Note over User,NB: Flow 2: User Accesses Notebook (Auth Mode)
    User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.3
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>HTTPS TLS (service cert)
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Token valid
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(verb=get, resource=notebooks)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA token
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Access granted
    KRBP->>NB: Forward to notebook<br/>HTTP localhost:8888<br/>X-Auth-Request-User header
    NB-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response (HTTPS)
    Gateway-->>User: Response (HTTPS TLS 1.3)

    Note over User,NB: Flow 3: Idle Notebook Culling
    loop Every IDLENESS_CHECK_PERIOD minutes
        KF->>NB: GET /api/kernels, /api/terminals<br/>HTTP 8888/TCP, no auth
        NB-->>KF: Activity status
    end
    Note right of KF: If idle > CULL_IDLE_TIME
    KF->>K8sAPI: Patch Notebook (stop annotation)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA token
    KF->>K8sAPI: Scale StatefulSet to 0<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA token
